{"tid":1360654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾志光同新華社講話去睇曼城唱歌既人係收左錢搞亂香港","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T12:07:17.000Z","uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"525743f6b47149263ee3c21d440fa124fb2c75cb","tid":1360654,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:43:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10162194683750230&amp;id=801620229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10162194683750230%26id%3D801620229&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9S%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=5c907113\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10162194683750230&amp;id=801620229</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大球場今晚上演傑志對曼城，球迷計劃分別在上下半場的21分鐘唱《Do You Hear The People Sing?》，抗議7月21日的元朗恐襲。<br />\n<br />\n賽前在記者室，見到鼎鼎大名、無綫電視的鍾志光，他對新華社記者表示，反送中的學生和年輕人必定有人指使，「呢班人一定係有人指使，收咗錢，咁多頭盔同物資。香港俾呢班人玩完。呢班友無大台？梗係唔信啦。」"},{"pid":"4af572a1bc3e3b14f7ab5f1eb7fb373910e34fd8","tid":1360654,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦"},{"pid":"d5a79a278eb3bcbb3e1fd1d9536b9b6a1733f208","tid":1360654,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4af572a1bc3e3b14f7ab5f1eb7fb373910e34fd8","tid":1360654,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:44:40.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母"},{"pid":"982e533198c258cecda6d56093b35212e65e7cd3","tid":1360654,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:45:10.000Z","msg":"叫解放軍黎鎮壓啦"},{"pid":"c4acd9bf1aae3ecc611246482d3df6c6f80b25fd","tid":1360654,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:45:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"a2081fd5652070ef037adf7837a99f9905b4a024","tid":1360654,"uid":132770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:46:31.0